{"title":"LeetCode-每日一题二分法，理解再次深刻-C++","uid":"13311aa294e657eaef79fbe3e5c5f789","slug":"LeetCode二分法","date":"2023-12-18T02:30:07.000Z","updated":"2023-12-19T01:27:18.082Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/LeetCode二分法.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"LeetCode-每日一题二分法，理解再次深刻-C\"><a href=\"#LeetCode-每日一题二分法，理解再次深刻-C\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LeetCode-每日一题二分法，理解再次深刻-C++\"></a>LeetCode-每日一题二分法，理解再次深刻-C++</h1><h1 id=\"162-寻找峰值\"><a href=\"#162-寻找峰值\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"162.寻找峰值\"></a><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/find-peak-element/description/\">162.寻找峰值</a></h1><blockquote>\n<p>峰值元素是指其值严格大于左右相邻值的元素。</p>\n<p>给你一个整数数组 <code>nums</code>，找到峰值元素并返回其索引。数组可能包含多个峰值，在这种情况下，返回 <strong>任何一个峰值</strong> 所在位置即可。</p>\n<p>你可以假设 <code>nums[-1] = nums[n] = -∞</code> 。</p>\n<p>你必须实现时间复杂度为 <code>O(log n)</code> 的算法来解决此问题。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">输入：nums = [1,2,3,1]</span><br><span class=\"line\">输出：2</span><br><span class=\"line\">解释：3 是峰值元素，你的函数应该返回其索引 2。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"1-1-做法1-0\"><a href=\"#1-1-做法1-0\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.1 做法1.0\"></a>1.1 做法1.0</h2><figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title class_\">Solution</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">findPeakElement</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt;&amp; nums)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//虽然是二分查找，但是根据-无穷，来提前却确定返回的信息也会跟关键</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>() == <span class=\"number\">1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(nums[<span class=\"number\">0</span>] &gt; nums[<span class=\"number\">1</span>])</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(nums[nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>()<span class=\"number\">-1</span>] &gt; nums[nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>()<span class=\"number\">-2</span>])</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>()<span class=\"number\">-1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> l = <span class=\"number\">0</span>, r = nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>()<span class=\"number\">-1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(l &lt;= r)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"type\">int</span> m = l+((r-l)&gt;&gt;<span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(nums[m] &lt; nums[m<span class=\"number\">-1</span>])</span><br><span class=\"line\">                r = m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(nums[m] &lt; nums[m+<span class=\"number\">1</span>])</span><br><span class=\"line\">                l = m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(nums[m] &gt; nums[m<span class=\"number\">-1</span>] &amp;&amp; nums[m] &gt; nums[m+<span class=\"number\">1</span>])</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>想明白和常规二分法的区别:</strong></p>\n<p>常规二分法去寻找答案，当m不符合的时候，一定可以根据“单调性”去推断，答案在当前的左侧(or 右侧)，并且通过<code>ans = m;</code>不断记录着最新符合要求的答案，最后返回ans即可</p>\n<p>但是本题，并不存在所谓的可以用来判断的单调性，而且答案可以说唯一，所以在里面添加最后一个if</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">else if(nums[m] &gt; nums[m-1] &amp;&amp; nums[m] &gt; nums[m+1])</span><br><span class=\"line\">    return m;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>一旦满足要求，直接return。在这个思路中，我们始终是把“每一循环的m”当作可能的答案去判断是否该return。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">if(nums[m] &lt; nums[m-1])</span><br><span class=\"line\">    r = m;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>此时根据高数的什么性质来着：</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312181042063.png\" alt=\"image-20231218104206070\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" />\n\n<p>中间一定是存在最值的，所以判断答案在左边，就把r移动到m了，但是，为什么不是m-1呢，因为m-1可能是答案，而且我们return 判断中是把答案作为中间元素，和左右两边元素比较的，所以<strong>不能让边界碰到“潜在的答案”</strong></p>\n<p><strong>也可以说：是return 的形式决定了转移的类型</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"2-1-做法2-0——三位一体\"><a href=\"#2-1-做法2-0——三位一体\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.1 做法2.0——三位一体\"></a>2.1 做法2.0——三位一体</h2><p>上面提到</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>也可以说：是return 的形式决定了转移的类型</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>这次换一个返回形式<code>return l</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title class_\">Solution</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">findPeakElement</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt;&amp; nums)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> n = nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(n == <span class=\"number\">1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> l = <span class=\"number\">0</span>, r = n<span class=\"number\">-1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(l &lt; r)&#123;       </span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"type\">int</span> m = l+((r-l)&gt;&gt;<span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(nums[m] &lt; nums[m+<span class=\"number\">1</span>])     <span class=\"comment\">//m一定不是答案，m+1可能是答案</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                l = m+<span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> </span><br><span class=\"line\">                r =  m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> l;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>这时的思路是，我最后结束循环的时候，<code>l m r</code>三位一体，都是指向“答案的”</p>\n<p>所以，第一点，我们要更改<code>while(l &lt; r)</code>，因为既然三位一体，那么相等的话，还会进行一次判断，再次移动</p>\n<p>看第二个改动</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">if(nums[m] &lt; nums[m+1])     //m一定不是答案，m+1可能是答案</span><br><span class=\"line\">    l = m+1;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>又提到三位一体，就是让l r这个边界，也坐落在“潜在的答案”上，这个和上面《<strong>不能让边界碰到“潜在的答案”</strong>》，有着本质的区别</p>\n<p>那第一个条件，应该怎么写呢，我可以判断m和m+1， m和m-1呀</p>\n<p>此时，就从两个元素入手，<code>l=0 m=0 r=1</code>。所以根据这里，更符合答案的普适，选择<code>nums[m] &lt; nums[m+1]</code>。</p>\n<p>m一定不是答案了此时的m+1，可能是答案，那就把左边界放到答案上面，促进后面的三位一体</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-1-总结\"><a href=\"#3-1-总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.1 总结\"></a>3.1 总结</h2><p>很棒，今天第三次来做这个题，还是有收获的，距离第一次做也正好两个月了</p>\n<p>1.0 是根据左神的思路来的，但是之前一直看到有2.0的出现，今天就好好分析了一波，真是<strong>横看成岭侧成峰啊</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312181058989.png\" alt=\"image-20231218105825819\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"1901-寻找峰值II\"><a href=\"#1901-寻找峰值II\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1901.寻找峰值II\"></a><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/find-a-peak-element-ii/description/\">1901.寻找峰值II</a></h1><blockquote>\n<p>很巧，今天又是二分，12.19</p>\n<p>而且也算是另一种形式的二分吧，也加进来了</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>一个 2D 网格中的 <strong>峰值</strong> 是指那些 <strong>严格大于</strong> 其相邻格子(上、下、左、右)的元素。</p>\n<p>给你一个 <strong>从 0 开始编号</strong> 的 <code>m x n</code> 矩阵 <code>mat</code> ，其中任意两个相邻格子的值都 <strong>不相同</strong> 。找出 <strong>任意一个 峰值</strong> <code>mat[i][j]</code> 并 <strong>返回其位置</strong> <code>[i,j]</code> 。</p>\n<p>你可以假设整个矩阵周边环绕着一圈值为 <code>-1</code> 的格子。</p>\n<p>要求必须写出时间复杂度为 <code>O(m log(n))</code> 或 <code>O(n log(m))</code> 的算法</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">输入: mat = [[1,4],[3,2]]</span><br><span class=\"line\">输出: [0,1]</span><br><span class=\"line\">解释: 3 和 4 都是峰值，所以[1,0]和[0,1]都是可接受的答案。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">输入: mat = [[10,20,15],[21,30,14],[7,16,32]]</span><br><span class=\"line\">输出: [1,1]</span><br><span class=\"line\">解释: 30 和 32 都是峰值，所以[1,1]和[2,2]都是可接受的答案</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"2-1-三位一体\"><a href=\"#2-1-三位一体\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.1 三位一体\"></a>2.1 三位一体</h2><figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//这是直接比较m行最大值和m+1行最大值，虽也能ac，但是证明感觉还是力不从心，没有比较[m][j] - [m][j+1]这种稳妥</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title class_\">Solution</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">findMaxNum</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt; &amp;nums)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> *<span class=\"built_in\">max_element</span>(nums.<span class=\"built_in\">begin</span>(), nums.<span class=\"built_in\">end</span>());</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">findMaxIndex</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt; &amp;v)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"built_in\">max_element</span>(v.<span class=\"built_in\">begin</span>(),v.<span class=\"built_in\">end</span>()) - v.<span class=\"built_in\">begin</span>(); </span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\">vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt; <span class=\"title\">findPeakGrid</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt;&gt;&amp; mat)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//灵神，以行号二分</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> n = mat.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(n == <span class=\"number\">1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> &#123;<span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"built_in\">findMaxIndex</span>(mat[<span class=\"number\">0</span>])&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> l = <span class=\"number\">0</span>, r = n<span class=\"number\">-1</span>;         <span class=\"comment\">//采用三位一体</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(l &lt; r)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"type\">int</span> m = l+((r-l)&gt;&gt;<span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"type\">int</span> maxnum = <span class=\"built_in\">findMaxNum</span>(mat[m]);        <span class=\"comment\">//m行的最大值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(maxnum &lt; <span class=\"built_in\">findMaxNum</span>(mat[m+<span class=\"number\">1</span>]))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                l = m+<span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">else</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                r = m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>&#123;l, <span class=\"built_in\">findMaxIndex</span>(mat[l])&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>把每行看做一个元素，就将二维的二分转为一维了</p>\n<p>那怎么把每行的看做一个呢——就找到每行最大的元素，如果<code>nums[m][j]</code>为m行最大元素，而他小于<code>nums[m+1][j]</code>，则根据性质，下面必然有答案，这里就和一维的一样了</p>\n<p>这是直接比较m行最大值和m+1行最大值，虽也能ac，但是证明感觉还是力不从心，没有比较<code>[m][j] - [m][j+1]</code>这种稳妥</p>\n","text":"LeetCode-每日一题二分法，理解再次深刻-C++162.寻找峰值 峰值元素是指其值严格大于左右相邻值的元素。 给你一个整数数组 nums，找到峰值元素并返...","permalink":"/post/LeetCode二分法","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"LeetCode","slug":"LeetCode","count":10,"path":"api/categories/LeetCode.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"LeetCode","slug":"LeetCode","count":10,"path":"api/tags/LeetCode.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#LeetCode-%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%80%E9%A2%98%E4%BA%8C%E5%88%86%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%8D%E6%AC%A1%E6%B7%B1%E5%88%BB-C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">LeetCode-每日一题二分法，理解再次深刻-C++</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#162-%E5%AF%BB%E6%89%BE%E5%B3%B0%E5%80%BC\"><span class=\"toc-text\">162.寻找峰值</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-1-%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%951-0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.1 做法1.0</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-1-%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%952-0%E2%8